额部分予以鸿卡补偿。详情请查看售后服务-<a href=\"http://www.tao3c.com/Info/InfoDetails.do?cid=53005\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-decoration:none;color:#484848;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#0000ff;\">售后条款</span></a>。<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n3、&nbsp; 机打发票<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n为保证您的合法权益，高鸿商城所有销售的商品均可开具正规机打发票，发票统一印有“北京大唐高鸿电子商贸有限公司”专用章，可作为商品保修的凭证。<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n4、&nbsp; 全场包邮<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n高鸿商城所有订单均享受在线支付免快递运费的优惠活动；白金（消费超过1万元）会员以上免快递运费。<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n您在购物过程中遇到任何问题，都可以联系我们的客服寻求帮助。<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n客服热线：400-650-9676&nbsp; (工作时间：周一至周五 8:30-20:00，周六日及法定节假日 9:00-18:00)</p>','1','2012-05-06 11:43:51','20100721001','ostocy','1','1','1',0,'html/default/article/201205060072.html',1,'新手指南','1','0','2012-05-06 11:43:51',0);
