e=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">3</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、高鸿商城提供的商品发票是“北京大唐高鸿电子商贸有限公司”发票，均为中文机打“商品专用发票”，用作单位报销或维修、退换货的凭证。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"color:#484848;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n</span><b style=\"color:#484848;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">如何获得增值税专用发票</b><span style=\"color:#484848;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\"><br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n1</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\"><span style=\"color:#484848;\">、国家对增值税专用发票有严格的规定，请企业客户（非个人用户）将《一般纳税人证书》、《营业执照》、《税务登记证》、《开户许可证》四类证件的扫描图发送至</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">ostocy@163.com</span></span><a href=\"mailto:zp@tao3c.com\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-decoration:none;color:#484848;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">邮箱，高鸿商城将由专门人员负责为您开具增值税发票。</span></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">2</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、根据国家相关规定，增值税发票内容只能选择商品明细，给您带来不便请您谅解。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">3</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、由于近期订单量激增，高鸿商城不能保证在每月25日前为企业客户开具增值税发票，但高鸿商城会尽其所能与税务部门沟通，尽快为您开具增值税发票，并在第一时间以快递方式为您寄出，给您带来不便请您谅解。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><b style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">开发票的注意事项</b></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">1</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、由于近期订单量激增，每月发票增量有限，目前，支付金额小于或等于50元将不开具普通发票。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">2</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、发票金额含配送费金额，鸿卡、购物券、积分等虚拟货币支付的金额将不开具发票。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">3、订单金额小于500元，不能开据增值税专用发票。（累计500元除外）</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">4、团购、拍卖、抢购订单、奥特莱斯订单、使用购物券的订单，不开据增值税专用发票。<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n</span><b style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">补寄或更换发票流程</b><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\"><br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n1</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、请您在自提点或者配送人员在场的情况下检查货物及发票，如未收到发票或发票信息错误，请当场向自提点人员或配送人员指出，并致电400-650-9676，由客服为您登记办理，</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">高鸿商城会自您登记补开发票之日起，两周内以快递的方式您寄出。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">2</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、如因高鸿商城原因所致发票信息错误，请您将原发票寄回我公司，由高鸿商