le-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-family:宋体;\">如何获得购物券</span></span></span></strong></p>\n<span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-family:宋体;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\">1、 赠券：商城中部分商品会赠送购物券。（随订单赠送的购物券不需要自己领取，订单完成后自动发送至用户账户中）；</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\">2、 活动发券：商城举行的部分促销活动，向会员发放一定数量和金额的购物券；</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\">3、 合作伙伴发券：高鸿商城与各种合作伙伴合作时，期中部分合作推广活动会有一定数量和金额的购物券进行发放。</p>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">如何使用购物券</span></span></span></strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">1、每订单只能使用一张购物券（包括所有种类购物券）；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">2、购物券不能转让、买卖；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">3、使用购物券交易中出现因客户原因造成的退、换货，所使用的购物券不予退还；非客户原因造成的退换货，使用的礼券返将由客服返还到用户帐户中；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">4、购物券有使用效期，请在有效期前使用，购物券过期将自动作废；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">5、团购、拍卖、秒杀、奥特莱斯等特价商品，以及限定不可使用购物券的商品，不可使用购物券进行购买；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">6、购物券无法支付运费金额；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">7、<span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#ff0000;\"><strong style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\">同一批次购物券，一个用户只能使用一张（套），如同一用户多次使用同一批次购物券购买同一属性商品，高鸿商城有权随时取消订单。<br style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n同一用户定义为包括但不限于同一ID、同一收货人、联系电话、收货地址等。</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;text-align:left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px