 ('2012051600357','戴尔（DELL）XPS14Z--328S 14英寸笔记本电脑','戴尔',NULL,'电脑办公','笔记本','',NULL,'201108160052','2012050600113','0',810,7600,7990,'/Uploads/20120516/2012051618114993350.jpg,/Uploads/20120516/2012051618115225280.jpg,/Uploads/20120516/2012051618115499906.jpg,',10,'1','<div class=\"prodetailtext mt10\" style=\"margin:10px 0px 0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;width:770px;float:left;font-family:宋体;color:#484848;line-height:normal;\"><div class=\"prodetailbox\" id=\"cont1\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:10px;list-style:none;width:750px;float:left;\"><div class=\"prodetailbox_title\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:20px 10px 10px;list-style:none;width:730px;background-image:url(http://tao3c.cn/datang/templets/Default/Default/images/prodetail_title.gif);font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;line-height:20px;background-position:50% 100%;background-repeat:repeat no-repeat;\"><span style=\"line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div class=\"prodetailtext\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;width:750px;float:left;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><h1 style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 12px;list-style:none;width:768px;background-color:#f8f8f8;border-left-color:#cacaca;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:1px;border-right-color:#cacaca;border-right-style:solid;border-right-width:1px;border-bottom-color:#ebebeb;border-bottom-style:solid;border-bottom-width:1px;font-size:0px;float:left;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;font-size:12px;\">New! XPS 14z笔记本电脑</span></h1>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;width:250px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;width:250px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">创•想无边</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">• 第二代酷睿i系列处理器<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n• 14寸高清无边框显示屏<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n• 13寸机身，极致轻薄便携</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">极致纤薄，无比强大</strong><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\nXPS 14z 笔记本电脑厚度为 0.9 英寸（ 23 毫米），起始重量为 4.36 磅 （ 1.98 千克），具备非凡的超薄设计。 但配备第 2 代英特尔 ® 酷睿 ™ 处理器，可提供卓越性能。 电池续航时间长达 6 小时 58 分钟，随时可以带着在路上使用。<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n&nbsp;<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">无边框设计</strong><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n窄边框显示屏和超薄铝制框架可使您全身心关注宽大的 14 英寸高清显示屏。 这一切尽在 13 英寸的纤巧机身中。<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">高性能显卡显威</strong><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\" />\n清晰锐利的图像仅仅是个开始。1G NVIDIA<sup style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">®</sup>GeForce<sup style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">®</sup>独立显卡等选项让您轻松体验引人入胜的 Web 内容，以及在支持 3D 功能的电视上营造逼真的 3D 体验。</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\"><img title=\"XPS 14z Laptop\" alt=\"XPS 14z Laptop\" src=\"http://i.dell.com/das/xa.ashx/global-site-design%20WEB/ebdfbf7b-c770-5c53-efab-12ead059863c/1/OriginalJPG?id=Dell/Product_Images/Dell_Client_Products/Notebooks/XPS_Notebooks/XPS_14z/overview/cn/lapt